{"tid":997160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大駐中國大使被炒魷","createTime":"2019-01-27T02:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T05:18:11.000Z","uid":41404,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6629e936d54ac5d9f4d6fbfb7962b626001274e0","tid":997160,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:39:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/mccallum-out-ambassador-1.4994492\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fmccallum-out-ambassador-1.4994492&d=VUGLEaUORJJ7MxxoyUgS9b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=96368a26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/mccallum-out-ambassador-1.4994492</a><br />\n<br />\nJohn McCallum has been fired as Canada's ambassador to China.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Last night I asked for and accepted John McCallum's resignation as Canada's Ambassador to China,&quot; Prime Minister Justin Trudeau said in a statement Saturday.<br />\n<br />\nA spokesperson for the prime minister confirmed Trudeau delivered the news to McCallum himself.<br />\n<br />\nThe statement didn't offer a reason for the removal, which comes in the middle of a diplomatic crisis with China. It caps off an especially tough week for McCallum after he controversially waded into the extradition request against Meng Wanzhou, an executive with Chinese telecom company Huawei."},{"pid":"9e0ef8daeb63f2f67954aad06cffe11363742c50","tid":997160,"uid":59898,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 提水俾支那<br />\n一係間諜一係苙水"},{"pid":"e59454f50056706f67365dc1af0a030f721f664c","tid":997160,"uid":10715,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T03:01:12.000Z","msg":"醒目仔<br />\n咁樣先可以趁未出事成家安全返到家鄉"},{"pid":"9be7734ea86266fe429f6e91f6db3b9f356bb115","tid":997160,"uid":1327,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01